united states area code 716 is an area code that is used for the western corner of new york , including buffalo , niagara falls and the surrounding area . the 716 area code was one of the original set of area codes issued in october 1947 , and originally included significant portions of central new york . in 1954 , area code 607 was created by splitting 716 and area code 315 . in 2001 , the new area code of 585 was created for the rochester area . until 1993 , it was bounded over the niagara river by area code 416 ( now 905 ) in ontario . the buffalo 716ers basketball team are named for the telephone area code . calls to god may be placed to 776-2323 , according to the cinema release of bruce almighty ; that number was removed from the video release & tv versions as , while it was ( and remains ) unassigned in buffalo 's area code 716 , it was routinely misdialled to other area codes as a nuisance call to actual subscribers .